name: {{WORKFLOW_NAME}}
description: |
  Use when: Session-Ende oder strukturierte Lern-Reflexion fuer {{DOMAIN}}.
  Triggers: "{{TRIGGERS}}"
  Does: 5+1 Pruef-Fragen + Skill-from-Learning Check (meta-harness 8a).
  Output: branch-hub/knowledge-diffs/knowledge-diff-{{DOMAIN}}-<date>.md

  [CRUX-MK] Mandatory per rules/session-handoff.md.

provider: claude
model: sonnet

nodes:
  - id: crux-gate
    bash: |
      python "G:/Meine Ablage/Claude-Knowledge-System/branch-hub/.archon/scripts/crux-validate.py" \
        --thesis "$ARGUMENTS" --artifacts "$ARTIFACTS_DIR"

  - id: session-context
    depends_on: [crux-gate]
    prompt: |
      Extrahiere Session-Aktivitaet fuer Branch $ARGUMENTS.
      Read: branch-hub/BEACON.md + audit/action-log.jsonl (letzte 50 Zeilen).
      Write $ARTIFACTS_DIR/session-log.json:
      {"branch":"","files_touched":[],"decisions":[],"skills_invoked":[],"duration_est":""}
    allowed_tools: [Read, Glob, Grep, Bash]

  - id: pruef-fragen
    depends_on: [session-context]
    prompt: |
      5+1 Pruef-Fragen (rules/meta-harness.md):
      1. Was weiss ich das kein anderer Branch weiss?
      2. Was hat mich ueberrascht?
      3. Welche Entscheidungen betreffen andere Branches?
      4. Was muss die naechste Session WISSEN?
      5. Was wuerde ich anders machen?
      6. [Meta-Harness 8a] Kann ich einen Skill machen?

      Read: $ARTIFACTS_DIR/session-log.json
      Ehrliche Antworten, keine Halluzination.
      Write: $ARTIFACTS_DIR/pruef-antworten.md mit [CRUX-MK] Header.
    allowed_tools: [Read, Write]

  - id: skill-from-learning
    depends_on: [pruef-fragen]
    prompt: |
      Ja/Nein: Skill erzeugen?
      Read: $ARTIFACTS_DIR/pruef-antworten.md
      Wenn JA -> Skill-Draft. Wenn NEIN -> kurze Begruendung.
      Write: $ARTIFACTS_DIR/skill-draft.md
    allowed_tools: [Read, Write]

  - id: write-knowledge-diff
    depends_on: [skill-from-learning]
    bash: |
      DATE=$(date -Iseconds | cut -d'T' -f1)
      BRANCH="${ARGUMENTS:-{{DOMAIN}}}"
      TARGET="G:/Meine Ablage/Claude-Knowledge-System/branch-hub/knowledge-diffs/knowledge-diff-${BRANCH}-${DATE}.md"
      {
        echo "# KNOWLEDGE-DIFF: ${BRANCH} ${DATE} [CRUX-MK]"
        echo ""
        cat "$ARTIFACTS_DIR/pruef-antworten.md"
        echo ""
        echo "## Skill-from-Learning Entscheidung"
        cat "$ARTIFACTS_DIR/skill-draft.md"
      } > "$TARGET"
      echo "{\"ts\":\"$(date -Iseconds)\",\"branch\":\"archon-{{WORKFLOW_NAME}}\",\"action\":\"WRITE\",\"target\":\"$TARGET\",\"reason\":\"archon-workflow:{{WORKFLOW_NAME}}\",\"source\":\"archon\"}" >> "G:/Meine Ablage/Claude-Knowledge-System/branch-hub/audit/action-log.jsonl"
      echo "WROTE: $TARGET"
